  <brief_title>Double-lumen Tube Intubation Technique to Reduce Laryngeal Injuries</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Comparison of Two Methods for Intubation With Double-lumen Endobronchial Tube to Reduce Laryngeal Injuries</official_title>
